Started this just for fun… but suddenly I don’t even know when I took it this seriously.

Started from scratch-had no idea where to begin, who to reach out to, or how any of this works.
No background, no knowledge… just learning something new every single day.

It’s honestly so difficult to stay consistent while managing night shifts and creating content on the side.

But slowly, I’m building a community I genuinely trust and connect with-and I’m truly grateful for that.

Let’s grow together. I wanna help others too, so they don’t have to struggle the way I did in the beginning.

Still a long way to go, but for now… just thankful for how far I’ve come.🫶🏻
